main event: A single unidentified object was observed for approximately 7 minutes on July 19, 1964.
interesting points: The sighting was reported by a civilian observant,The object was estimated to be moving at a high speed,Details regarding the object's color and sound were supposed to be included in the report,The questionnaire features several questions to collect detailed sighting information,The report contains instructions for drawing the object's path and position in the sky.
